    </sentence>
    <sentence id="DDI-DrugBank.d573.s2" text="Where this is not possible, minoxidil therapy should be started in the hospital and the patient should remain institutionalized until severe orthostatic effects are no longer present or the patient has learned to avoid activities that provoke them.">
